      <title>关税担忧引发白银和铜市场脱节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/trump-tariff-fears-spark-disconnect-in-silver-and-copper-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员加大对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 将对金属征收高额进口关税的押注，作为其全球贸易战升级的一部分，纽约的铜和白银期货价格飙升至竞争对手的国际价格基准之上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/trump-tariff-fears-spark-disconnect-in-silver-and-copper-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
